{
  "stem": "1518.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Anyway, with these woods, we-- we started to go like east and we wound up closer.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The-- the Russians were coming closer, and we wound up by [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We met with the Russian army.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would say there were at least 50, about that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was one.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was-- there was one leader.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They called him capitan.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "His name?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think was Bialov.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were-- there were so many, it's very hard to remember.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We didn't have any weapons at the time, but-- but when-- as we went like, north, like, through every village, when we used to-- before we used to go in, I used to go in and check out to see if, you know, if there's German army, the police, and how many is there, what-- if we can stay for a while.",
      "word_count": 62
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, near coming for food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because sometimes they had German-- the army concentration, like for the army.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We wouldn't go in there with too many.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But if there was no army stationed there, just the Ukrainian police, we used to go in there at night for food and shelter, whatever we can get.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then we-- then we-- they-- they-- they got a few guns, you know, from the Germans, like surprises-- like small arms.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We didn't-- we didn't have-- with what?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, that's-- obviously.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But later on-- later on, when before the end, we had a few guns already.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we used to, like, on-- on-- on the way-- like, if there were just, let's say, one German wagon, or two, we used to attack them.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Like take whatever they had and kill the-- the Germans.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But we didn't-- we couldn't attack, let's say it was a whole company, battalion.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was no way.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
